com.vmware.vapi.data

Class DataDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.vapi.data.DataDefinition
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnyErrorDefinition, BlobDefinition, BooleanDefinition, DoubleDefinition, DynamicStructDefinition, IntegerDefinition, ListDefinition, OpaqueDefinition, OptionalDefinition, SecretDefinition, StringDefinition, StructDefinition, StructRefDefinition, VoidDefinition

    public abstract class DataDefinition
extends Object
    The DataDefinition class is an abstract base class for all types in the vAPI run-time type system.

        Returns:
